識過世面? <br />\n就係試過咁多野之後，發現讀書係依家唯一要專心做既野。 好心你喇，無論係返學，or返緊工都好，專心左你眼前既野再搞其他野喇，好嗎?"},{"pid":"4227573ccf5b061c1e5cf86bfbeacf69c39ea00c","tid":402894,"uid":147797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自資有錢就畢業  正常都會比人睇唔起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家唔係講緊畢唔畢到業，而係可唔可以first Hon 畢業呀，你估坐係到咩都唔做就first Hon到?"},{"pid":"ee0a8c406e329a5ccae255f75172ab72224f65a6","tid":402894,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想搵到戰友一齊讀書，由中學已經成日自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你讀緊咩?"},{"pid":"7104c0bb8ba38abf78c760986a1010f4c1faff6e","tid":402894,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打讀咩科？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEducation"},{"pid":"b40b9cf4a69ddc6c1c578b37dac5bf289e26dbf4","tid":402894,"uid":143400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年由highdip升上左大學year3, 讀緊自資學位，我想講越係比其他人睇唔起，就越要去提升自己，令當時睇唔起你既人</blockquote><br />\n你highdip上自資咋，你以為你上左資助學位咩。<br />\n本身見樓主講到好似而家勁過當時睇你唔起嘅人，點知原來都係上返資助學位咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ee9aea7e9b02a319f4d6d41b28d8c344200033","tid":402894,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家做assessment 一派就開始做，完全唔會hea,因為知道比左咁多錢讀，無firstHon同倒錢落海無分別! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n??"},{"pid":"5604f2e1f3b3d5c02526bdc6457a510212403b64","tid":402894,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今年由highdip升上左大學year3, 讀緊自資學位，我想講越係比其他人睇唔起，就越要去提升自己，令當時睇唔起你既人</blockquote><br />\n你highdip上自資咋，你以為你上左資助學位咩。<br />\n本身見樓主講到好似而家勁過當時睇你唔起嘅人，點知原來都係上返資助學位咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打錯字，前言不對後語，send出來之前又唔對一對，都知你咩料喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167168dde1eeec9b84e6ba4648e6c7de453dc7e7","tid":402894,"uid":22359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"想問下巴打平時點樣自修英文?我今年HD year 2 英文仲好廢 有咩溫習方法建議"},{"pid":"8d6a4b1d31989eb802c132487d8c7b8960f986ce","tid":402894,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下巴打平時點樣自修英文?我今年HD year 2 英文仲好廢 有咩溫習方法建議</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩唔識寫落本筆記到，得閒拎出來睇下，最重要係記底你讀緊既科既term同埋生字。最最最重要真係對多D，唔好驚，當習慣，慢慢識明晒架喇~"},{"pid":"77334216b35a8c809a596ef166a33b4e2bdc6f2f","tid":402894,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"樓主咩major要做咁多assessment"},{"pid":"4e7272a34bd4c1a4b93b57b2f19ca4ce3464d4e6","tid":402894,"uid":146538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"好搞笑，一個人發奮都會比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁驚人勤力咪自己勤力過樓主囖<br />\n唔明有乜好打擊同質疑"},{"pid":"2e777690877a19f96b7f8c1d6a8e62647f262006","tid":402894,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n自資學位真係你做唔做都wfc"},{"pid":"3238b741f2e741159c3467a582d56ea4ddfdaa9b","tid":402894,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好搞笑，一個人發奮都會比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁驚人勤力咪自己勤力過樓主囖<br />\n唔明有乜好打擊同質疑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝你既支持"},{"pid":"95688959efa2ede4bcad7751bfa6f0917700130d","tid":402894,"uid":72093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"你hd果陣點過？同埋自資係本地定外國"},{"pid":"342e8271289b47f0d96aa340bc7820b9facebcfd","tid":402894,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc